BS_image: img-fluid  Description   Create responsive images by adding an .img-fluid class to the &lt;img&gt; tag. The image will then scale nicely to the parent element.
 Syntax  &lt;img class=&quot;img-fluid&quot; src=&quot;img_chania.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Chania&quot;&gt;  BS_Spacing: my  Description   Assign responsive-friendly margin or padding values to an element or a subset of its sides with shorthand classes
 Syntax  &lt;div class=&quot;my&quot;&gt; Centered element &lt;/div&gt;

